records.addlTxt:
Defendant Zachary J.T. Lechner in court with attorney Theodore F. Mazza.  James T. Sempf appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Court reviews rights, charges and penalties. Def enters NC plea to Ct 1 as charged. Court accepts plea and finds guilty. ADA Sempf heard. Atty Mazza heard. Court heard and imposes sentence:

1 yr probation w/h;
DNA sample and surcharge;
Right to expunge DNA sample if meets criteria;
Costs; 
All Financial obligations shall be paid to the Clerk of Courts within 60 days unless a payment plan is established.
